    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Positive transparencies in mounts suitable for projection, usually 35mm film in a mount of 2 by 2 inches. An image on film or glass, usually positive, intended to be viewed by means of light passing through the image and base using a viewer or projector.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
